1
00:00:00,580 --> 00:00:02,290
This is for you.

2
00:00:02,290 --> 00:00:03,630
What's this?

3
00:00:03,630 --> 00:00:05,460
I saw you couldn't decide on a color earlier.

4
00:00:06,090 --> 00:00:08,300
It's the lipstick shade
you didn't end up getting.

5
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:09,380
Are you sure?

6
00:00:10,140 --> 00:00:11,970
Wow! Thank you!

7
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:14,010
Go on, try it.

8
00:00:14,010 --> 00:00:15,430
Okay.

9
00:00:20,770 --> 00:00:21,730
How does it look?

10
00:00:22,270 --> 00:00:23,940
It looks great on you.

11
00:00:24,770 --> 00:00:25,570
But...

12
00:00:26,690 --> 00:00:28,190
You smudged it a little.

13
00:00:28,190 --> 00:00:30,740
(He's so casual when he touches me...)

14
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:32,570
(But it still makes my heart pound.)

15
00:00:32,570 --> 00:00:33,990
There. Perfect.

16
00:00:33,990 --> 00:00:35,790
I actually got something for you, too.

17
00:00:39,210 --> 00:00:40,710
Here, this is for you.

18
00:00:40,710 --> 00:00:42,130
What is it?

19
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:46,550
I thought if you held onto this,
your hand wouldn't hurt so much.

20
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:51,260
Thank you. I'll treasure it.

21
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:53,930
It's so cute.

22
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:57,680
(This contrast between his handsome looks
and his sweet, boyish personality...)

23
00:00:57,680 --> 00:01:00,640
(Any girl would fall for him.)

24
00:01:03,310 --> 00:01:06,400
(Huh? What is this feeling...?)

25
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:11,740
Well, I'll see you tomorrow.
Just let me know if you have any questions about makeup.

26
00:01:12,450 --> 00:01:13,950
Okay.

27
00:01:19,330 --> 00:01:21,000
(That woman...)
